overview:
BookedIN is an online appointment scheduling and payment system for small business. We make it easy to get noticed, get booked and get paid!

BookedIN is cloud based, so it’s up and running 24/7, anyone that has access to the internet from a computer, tablet or mobile device can access BookedIN.

BookedIN helps Small Businesses get more clients, increase repeat business, collect payments, reduce no-shows, and schedule from anywhere anytime.

BookedIN is a one stop business solution for Small Services based businesses by providing a booking web page, integration with Facebook or a business own website via a booking button, multi functional calendar, email reminders, payments services and so much more…

BookedIN has everything a business needs to get up and running in a fast and easy way.
